{"tid":869713,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"點解只係得馬鞍山線列車 右邊路軌向前行 左邊路軌向後行？","createTime":"2018-10-20T13:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T08:46:57.000Z","uid":26418,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"234901ab8a93f8d8d99033b3239c4a56c1d911f8","tid":869713,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"例如係荃灣線 荃灣站 / 觀塘線 觀塘站 / 東涌線 南昌站 / 火車 九龍塘站 <br />\n左邊路軌都係向前 右邊路軌都係向後<br />\n<br />\n唯獨馬鐵..好似車公廟站咁<br />\n右邊路軌先係向前 左邊路軌先係向後<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecb628fac10d7fa5ca46538ea839d2bbe6bf75f","tid":869713,"uid":33727,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"為左大圍轉車方便"},{"pid":"ce1149f4e5a6e42ef401c66090f8a695fdd30eed","tid":869713,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"9ecb628fac10d7fa5ca46538ea839d2bbe6bf75f","tid":869713,"uid":33727,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"為左大圍轉車方便"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"咁只係方面 馬鞍山去大圍轉車<br />\n如果搭火車去大圍轉馬鐵 一樣麻煩<br />\n<br />\n調轉左行 就麻煩到馬鐵轉火車<br />\n但就方便到火車轉馬鐵<br />\n<br />\n其實總會麻煩到其中一邊嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fd1550782ca31cd5d6e43fa82f6f9991a9c6b3","tid":869713,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1149f4e5a6e42ef401c66090f8a695fdd30eed","tid":869713,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"9ecb628fac10d7fa5ca46538ea839d2bbe6bf75f","tid":869713,"uid":33727,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:34:25.000Z","msg":"為左大圍轉車方便"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"咁只係方面 馬鞍山去大圍轉車<br />\n如果搭火車去大圍轉馬鐵 一樣麻煩<br />\n<br />\n調轉左行 就麻煩到馬鐵轉火車<br />\n但就方便到火車轉馬鐵<br />\n<br />\n其實總會麻煩到其中一邊嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"*